    <item>
      <title>爱立信价值下跌，一年内第二次对 Vonage 进行减记</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ericsson-takes-second-vonage-writedown-in-a-year-as-value-sinks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱立信公司警告投资者，由于 Vonage Holdings Corp. 的业绩恶化，该公司将在第二季度计提 114 亿瑞典克朗（11 亿美元）的非现金减值，这是不到一年内该资产第二次大幅减值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ericsson-takes-second-vonage-writedown-in-a-year-as-value-sinks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受人工智能推动，日本芯片设备销售额本财年有望增长 15%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/japan-chip-gear-sales-seen-climbing-15-this-fiscal-year-on-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家行业组织表示，得益于人工智能推动内存容量支出的复苏，日本芯片制造工具的销售额预计将在 2025 年 3 月之前增长 15%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/japan-chip-gear-sales-seen-climbing-15-this-fiscal-year-on-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:03:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非航空重建期间关注美国和欧洲航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-africa-airways-to-add-64-new-destinations-as-it-rebuilds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与投资者的交易失败后，南非航空公司正在重建业务，将重点放在地区和国际航线上，计划在 4 月底之前从其位于约翰内斯堡的枢纽增加非洲大陆的更多目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-africa-airways-to-add-64-new-destinations-as-it-rebuilds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 05:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大在美国报复威胁下实施数字服务税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国警告称将采取贸易报复措施，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府仍批准对大型外国科技公司征收数字服务税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易紧张局势升级，中国电动汽车捍卫欧洲市场份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/chinese-ev-brands-including-byd-saic-defend-europe-share-amid-trade-friction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新一轮关税出台以保护本土汽车制造商免受低成本进口产品冲击之前，中国电动汽车品牌 5 月份在低迷的欧洲电动汽车市场中仍保住了自己的份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/chinese-ev-brands-including-byd-saic-defend-europe-share-amid-trade-friction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
